<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<title>My Hometown – Nagpur</title>

<style>
:root {
      --bg: #0f2027;
      --bg-accent: #203a43;
      --bg-light: #2c5364;
      --text: #f2f6f8;
      --accent: #ffcc66;
      --muted: #cbd6dc;
    }

body {
margin: 0;
font-family: "Segoe UI", Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
color: var(--text);
background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg), var(--bg-accent), var(--bg-light));
    }

    .page {
max-width: 1000px;
margin: auto;
padding: 24px;
    }

header {
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
gap: 20px;
align-items: center;
padding: 24px;
border-radius: 16px;
background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    }

header h1 {
color: var(--accent);
    }

    .hero-img {
width: 100%;
height: 240px;
object-fit: cover;
border-radius: 12px;
    }

section {
margin-top: 28px;
padding: 20px;
border-radius: 14px;
background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    }

section h2 {
color: var(--accent);
    }

    .places {
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
gap: 15px;
margin-top: 15px;
    }

    .place-card {
background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
padding: 10px;
border-radius: 10px;
text-align: center;
    }

    .place-card img {
width: 100%;
height: 140px;
object-fit: cover;
border-radius: 10px;
    }

footer {
text-align: center;
margin-top: 30px;
color: var(--muted);
    }

    @media (max-width: 760px) {
header {
grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
</style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="page">

<header>
<div>
<h1>Welcome to Nagpur</h1>
<p>Known as the Orange City, Nagpur blends heritage, lakes, and greenery.</p>
</div>
<img class="hero-img" src="https://pbs.twimg.com/media/E2NG6wfVgAAgYnS.jpg" alt="Nagpur City" />
</header>

<section>
<h2>About my hometown</h2>
<p>
        Nagpur is located in Maharashtra and is famous for oranges, lakes, and cultural heritage.
</p>
</section>

<section>
<h2>Places to visit</h2>

<div class="places">

<div class="place-card">
<img src="https://as2.ftcdn.net/jpg/06/40/13/59/1000_F_640135967_9nsWSpfSI9TmxbZRSiCl05AxI6jCe9xL.jpg" alt="Deekshabhoomi">
<p>Deekshabhoomi</p>
</div>

<div class="place-card">
<img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSdW9empirByKx-NA-FqOSj08mgVC3SZifaxg&s" alt="Ambazari Lake">
<p>Ambazari Lake</p>
</div>

<div class="place-card">
<img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSy2GlcXAw0f5fjsEQsita2rpxLMKljdrG-8w&s" alt="Futala Lake">
<p>Futala Lake</p>
</div>

<div class="place-card">
<img src="https://nagpurtourism.co.in/images/places-to-visit/header/seminary-hills-nagpur-header-nagpur-tourism.jpg" alt="Seminary Hill">
<p>Seminary Hill</p>
</div>

<div class="place-card">
<img src="https://nagpurtourism.co.in/images/tourist-places/japanese-rose-garden-nagpur/japanese-rose-garden-nagpur-entry-ticket-price-nagpur-tourism.jpg" alt="Japanese Rose Garden">
<p>Japanese Rose Garden</p>
</div>

<div class="place-card">
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/23/Zero_mile_nagpur.jpg" alt="Zero Mile">
<p>Zero Mile</p>
</div>

</div>
</section>

<section>
<h2>Local flavors</h2>
<p>Famous for oranges, street food, and Maharashtrian dishes.</p>
</section>

<section>
<h2>Why I love it</h2>
<p>Peaceful environment, beautiful lakes, and friendly people.</p>
</section>

<footer>
      © My Hometown — Nagpur
</footer>

</div>
</body>
</html>
